        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/e/cdc98d/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2015-06-24T06:35:27.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>These have been a bit tight when the corked was pulled, but the wine opened up within 15-30 minutes and showed very well after that. I\u2019d say open one up\u2026esp since the premox record here isn\u2019t well understood (to me anyways), tho they act like premox won\u2019t be a problem. When did that mean anything tho. I\u2019d give it a double decant just before dinner if you can.</p>",
