      {
        "id": 1693832,
        "name": "john stimson",
        "username": "john_stimson",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/j/3d9bf3/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2015-06-24T14:57:43.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I\u2019ve consumed about eight of my twelve bottles.  for some reason, premier cru was posting this off on weekend specials (I think mine was $28, or maybe 32), and then actually supplying the wine.</p>\n<p>It\u2019s a great deal, and showing quite well now.  Mine have fattened up a bit.  I\u2019d suggest going ahead and trying one.  Love the style and love the producer.  Recent prices have risen and they seem harder to get, though.</p>",
